title: Cherchez l'erreur (1980 French film) When Bureaucrats Blunder | A Comedy of Errors

sources.title: Cherchez l'erreur (1980 French film) When Bureaucrats Blunder | A Comedy of Errors
sources.description:
Paul and his lively companions, including the intriguing Igor and the astute Solange, find themselves entangled in a lively quest to uncover the error that's unraveling their meticulously laid plans. As The Director intensifies the pressure, they cleverly navigate a series of amusing obstacles, blending wit and humor in a spirited race to correct the mishap.

Original title: Cherchez l'erreur

Director: Serge Korber
Writers: Roland Magdane

Main cast:
Roland Magdane - Paul
Roland Dubillard - Igor, the minister
Henri Virlojeux - The director
Micheline Luccioni - Solange

Genres: French cinema, Comedy
Release date: 22 October 1980
